<l>naviṟoṟu nūṉayam pōlum payiṟoṟum</l>
<l>paṇpuṭai yāḷar toṭarpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like learning, the friendship of the noble, the more it is cultivated, the more delightful does it become.</l>
